TopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_5644376\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 02, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104urf1665702988371.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/urf1665702988371.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/urf1665702988371.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"urf1665702988371\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Tab Key Behavior\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"urf1665702988371__p_d64493e1_d64494e1_d64495e1\">The default (USYS) keyboard translation tables define the following behavior for the Tab key:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"urf1665702988371__li_d27908e1_d27909e1_d27910e1\">When not in Zoom mode:\n <ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"urf1665702988371__li_d27911e1_d27912e1_d27913e1\">Tab is defined as ^FIELD.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"urf1665702988371__li_d27914e1_d27915e1_d27916e1\">^FIELD is defined as ^NEXT_FIELD or ^PREV_FIELD.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"urf1665702988371__li_d27917e1_d27918e1_d27919e1\">GOLD Tab is defined as a normal tab character.\n </li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"urf1665702988371__li_d27920e1_d27921e1_d27922e1\">When in Zoom mode:\n <ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"urf1665702988371__li_d27923e1_d27924e1_d27925e1\">Tab is defined as the ^HT (horizontal tab) character.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"urf1665702988371__li_d27926e1_d27927e1_d27928e1\">^FIELD is defined as the ^HT character.\n </li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"urf1665702988371__p_d64496e1_d64497e1_d64498e1\">In Zoom mode, Uniface converts any ^FIELD definition to a ^HT character since it is then impossible to go to the previous or next field. In this way, the Tab key can be used for both the functions to which computer users are accustomed.</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"urf1665702988371__note_w9094ab1b5b7_w9095ab1b5_w9096ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> The definitions for Tab and ^FIELD can be changed if required. If you do\n         change the behavior, remember to make the definitions after the mapping of\n            <code class=\"ph codeph\">^GOLD_BASE_SET</code>.</div>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_5644376\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_5644376\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Tab Key Behavior Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 02, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Tab Key Behavior The default (USYS) keyboard translation tables define the following behavior for the Tab key: When not in Zoom mode: Tab is defined as ^FIELD. ^FIELD is defined as ^NEXT_FIELD or ^PREV_FIELD. GOLD Tab is defined as a normal tab character. When in Zoom mode: Tab is defined as the ^HT (horizontal tab) character. ^FIELD is defined as the ^HT character. In Zoom mode, Uniface converts any ^FIELD definition to a ^HT character since it is then impossible to go to the previous or next field. In this way, the Tab key can be used for both the functions to which computer users are accustomed. Note: The definitions for Tab and ^FIELD can be changed if required. If you do change the behavior, remember to make the definitions after the mapping of ^GOLD_BASE_SET . Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}